title: Person of Interest 5x13 Sneak Peek "Return 0" (HD) Series Finale
author: televisionpromosdb
comment: Great ending to a superb show. I see Return 0 has a perfect 10 rating on IMDB, let's see if it holds. I think the Breaking Bad episode Ozymandias is the only tv episode that has managed to maintain a perfect 10 rating in the long run.
Oh my god! John has finally been made? Oh man! I cant believe this show is ending tomorrow!

Cop: Pulls gun
John: Rolls eyes "Really?"

Proceeds to take him out.
description:
Person of Interest 5x13 "Return 0" (Series Finale) Sneak Peek - Finch, Reese, Fusco and Shaw embark on one last mission to prevent Samaritan from destroying The Machine and cementing its hold over mankind, on the series finale of PERSON OF INTEREST, Tuesday, June 21st on CBS.
